### Axum Router Example with Various Routes

Source: https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum/blob/axum-v0.8.4/axum/src/docs/routing/route.md

A comprehensive example demonstrating various route definitions including static paths, captures, wildcards, and multiple methods.

```rust
use axum::{Router, routing::{get, delete}, extract::Path};

